resources.string: 2) Geli magaca iimaylka iyo furaha sirta ah ee leh ugu yaraan 1 xaraf weyn, 1 xaraf yar, 1 lambar, iyo 1 calaamad.
1) Guji badhanka si aad ugu darto ciyaaryahan cusub. .
2) Guji oblect-ka ku jira keydka macluumaadka si aad u cusbooneysiiso.
3) Guji badhanka tirtirka si aad uga saarto shayga.
